title: Lamoureux twins named to USA roster for Four Nations Cup
text:
Lamoureux twins named to USA roster for Four Nations Cup in Sweden in November THE ASSOCIATED PRESS   11:41 amLast   11:41 am   
Subjects: 
North Dakota (276) 

GRAND FORKS, North Dakota — Former University of North Dakota stars Monique Lamoureux (LAM'-uh-roo) and twin sister Jocelyn Lamoureux-Davidson are among 23 players named to the USA Hockey roster for the Four Nations Cup. 
The U.S will compete against Canada, Finland and host Sweden Nov. 4-8. 
The U.S. team will hold a camp in Chicago later this month before heading overseas.
